data.name: customSqlQuery5.Sql

data.name: customSqlQuery6.Sql
data.value: SELECT INVOICE_HDR_GKEY, INVOICE_ID, METAL, AVG(INVL_BILLED_PRICE) AS GBILLEDPRICE, SUM([PROD_QTY]) AS GTOTQTY, SUM([PROD_GROSS_WEIGHT]) AS GTOTGROSSWT, SUM([PROD_NET_WEIGHT]) AS GTOTNETWT, SUM([INVL_TOTAL]) AS GLINETOTAL FROM INVOICE_LINE WHERE INVOICE_ID = @paramInvNbr5 AND METAL = 'GOLD' GROUP BY INVOICE_HDR_GKEY,INVOICE_ID,METAL

data.name: customSqlQuery7.Sql
data.value: SELECT INVOICE_HDR_GKEY,INVOICE_ID, METAL, AVG(INVL_BILLED_PRICE) AS G18BILLEDPRICE, SUM([PROD_QTY]) AS G18TOTQTY, SUM([PROD_GROSS_WEIGHT]) AS G18TOTGROSSWT, SUM([PROD_NET_WEIGHT]) AS G18TOTNETWT, SUM([INVL_TOTAL]) AS G18LINETOTAL FROM INVOICE_LINE WHERE INVOICE_ID = @paramInvNbr18K AND METAL in ('GOLD.18KT') GROUP BY INVOICE_HDR_GKEY,INVOICE_ID,METAL

data.name: customSqlQuery8.Sql
